<h3 class="sectionedit3"><a name="notes" id="notes">Notes:</a></h3>
<div class="level3">

<p>

Bit set is missing two boolean queries to complement <code><a href="any" class="wikilink1" title="container:bitset:any">any()</a></code> and <code><a href="none" class="wikilink1" title="container:bitset:none">none()</a></code>: <code>all()</code> and <code>some()</code>.

</p>
<ul>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> all: <code>(~bitset).none()</code></div>
</li>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> some: <code>(~bitset).any()</code></div>
</li>
</ul>

</div>
